stories.title: We have had two poor days: Hooper
stories.summary:
A little old lady last night suggested that Cable & Wireless extend
its offer of voluntary severance packages beyond its employees

stories.title: Eight wicket win gives South Africa 3-1 lead in one-day series
stories.summary:
South Africa drew maximum reward from a hard weekend of cricket as they beat
the West Indies by eight wickets in the fourth one-day international at
Queen's Park stadium on Sunday and took a healthy 3-1 lead in the seven-match series
